subtitle: The <span style="color: [+ other_colour +];">**Others**</span> are a little conservative
on-arrival: baden_coalition_r = baden_coalition_r += true_other_r_baden; baden_true_others = "government"
go-to: baden_coalition_creator

@baden_invite_wp
view-if: wp_r_baden > 0 and not baden_wp = "government"
choose-if: dvp_relation >= 80 and baden_kpd == "opposition" and baden_sapd == "opposition" and baden_uspd == "opposition"
subtitle: The <span style="color: #b8996f;">**WP**</span> are a little conservative
